description:
Verve Records arranged a lunch with Joe at the Top of The Senator in Toronto this coming on the release of 'Lush Life' the music of Billy Strayhorn.
The interview was conducted by Bill King for the Jazz Report Magazine.
fulltitle: A Conversation with Joe Henderson (Jazz Report Magazine 1993)
title: A Conversation with Joe Henderson (Jazz Report Magazine 1993)
